<title>USA: PureTec Corp year loss narrows.</title>
<headline>PureTec Corp year loss narrows.</headline>
<dateline>RIDGEFIELD, N.J. 1996-10-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Shr	loss   $0.32	   loss   $0.95</p>
<p> Net	loss   8,173	   loss   16,908</p>
<p> Oper shr profit 0.04	    loss   0.09</p>
<p> Oper net profit 1,736	   loss   1,646</p>
<p> Revs		344,847		  52,324</p>
<p> Avg shrs	  27,268		   17,751</p>
<p>	 (All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: The company said Q4 data was not ready because it needed time to create proforma 1995 Q4 results to include the merger between PureTech International and Ozite Corp.</p>
<p>Net fiscal 1996 results included one-time $8.6 million charge due to shutdown of certain facilities.</p>
<p>Net fiscal 1995 results included $4.8 million loss from discontinued operations.</p>
<p>Excluding one-time charges, PureTec had 1996 oper earnings of $0.04 per share.</p>
<p>Fiscal 1995 results are before the merger. If the merger had occuRred at the start of fiscal 1995, the company would have had a proforma loss of $0.93 per share, including one-time charges.</p>
